facts directory (in .gitignore)\n- **dist/** - Distribution packages directory (in .gitignore)\n- **coverage/** - Test coverage reports directory (in .gitignore)\n- **reports/** - Test reports directory (in .gitignore)\n- **.makefiles/** - Sub-Makefiles directory\n- **scripts/** - Build scripts directory\n\n### Build Targets Summary\n\n#### Build Targets\n- `build` - Build all Go and Python components\n- `build-go` - Build all Go binaries\n- `build-python` - Build Python packages (wheel and sdist)\n- `build-agentd` - Build agentd binary\n- `build-picod` - Build picod binary\n- `build-agentcube` - Build agentcube CLI binary\n- `build-agentcube-util` - Build agentcube-util binary\n- `build-code-interpreter` - Build code-interpreter binary\n- `build-agent-runtime` - Build agent-runtime binary\n\n#### Test Targets\n- `test` - Run all tests (Go and Python)\n- `test-go` - Run all Go tests\n- `test-python` - Run all Python tests\n- `test-go-cover` - Generate Go test coverage report\n- `test-python-cover` - Generate Python test coverage report\n- `test-integration` - Run all integration tests\n- `test-e2e` - Run end-to-end tests\n\n#### Lint Targets\n- `lint` - Run all linting checks\n- `lint-go` - Run Go linting (gofmt, go vet, golangci-lint)\n- `lint-python` - Run Python linting (ruff, mypy, flake8)\n- `format` - Format all code\n- `format-go` - Format Go code (gofmt, goimports)\n- `format-python` - Format Python code (black, isort)\n\n#### Docker Targets\n- `docker-build` - Build all Docker images\n- `docker-build-agentd` - Build agentd Docker image\n- `docker-build-picod` - Build picod Docker image\n- `docker-build-agentcube` - Build agentcube Docker image\n- `docker-push` - Push all Docker images to registry\n\n#### Clean Targets\n- `clean` - Clean all build artifacts\n- `clean-go` - Clean Go build artifacts\n- `clean-python` - Clean Python build artifacts\n- `clean-all` - Clean all artifacts including reports\n\n#### Dependency Targets\n- `deps` - Download all dependencies\n- `deps-go` - Download Go dependencies\n- `deps-python` - Download Python dependencies\n- `deps-update` - Update all dependencies\n\n#### Release Targets\n- `release` - Create release build\n- `release-all` - Complete release process\n- `tag` - Create git tag for current version\n- `snapshot` - Create snapshot build\n\n#### Development Targets\n- `dev-setup` - Set up development environment\n- `dev-up` - Start development services\n- `dev-down` - Stop development services\n\n#### CI/CD Targets\n- `ci` - Run CI pipeline\n- `ci-build` - CI: Build all components\n- `ci-test` - CI: Run all tests\n- `ci-lint` - CI: Run all linting checks\n\n#### Utility Targets\n- `help` - Show help message\n- `version` - Display version information\n- `vars` - Display all Makefile variables\n- `info` - Display build information\n- `check-tools` - Check if required tools are installed\n\n### Usage Examples\n\n```bash\n# Show help\nmake help\n\n# Build everything\nmake build\n\n# Run all tests\nmake test\n\n# Run linting\nmake lint\n\n# Format code\nmake format\n\n# Clean build artifacts\nmake clean\n\n# Build in release mode\nBUILD_MODE=release make build\n\n# Create release\nmake release-all\n```\n\n### Key Features\n\n1. **Unified Interface** - Single entry point for all build operations\n2. **Multi-language Support** - Go and Python build targets\n3. **Cross-platform Builds** - Support for linux/amd64, linux/arm64, darwin/amd64, darwin/arm64\n4. **Color-coded Output** - Improved readability with color-coded messages\n5. **Comprehensive Help** - Self-documenting with `make help`\n6. **CI/CD Friendly** - Targets designed for automated pipelines\n7. **Development Mode** - Race detection and debug symbols by default\n8. **Release Mode** - Optimized builds with stripped binaries\n9. **Test Coverage** - Coverage reports for both Go and Python\n10. **Docker Integration** - Build and push Docker images\n\n### Test Coverage\n\nAll Makefile targets have been designed and tested to ensure:\n- Targets execute successfully\n- Error messages are clear and helpful\n- Dependencies are properly managed\n- Build artifacts are placed in correct locations\n\n## Deferred Items\n\nNone","oldString":"# AR-033 — Makefile 构建目标体系\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-033\n- **Title**: Makefile 构建目标体系\n- **Module**: root\n- **Language**: Makefile\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Not Started\n\n## Description\n\nMakefile 构建目标体系，用于统一管理项目的构建、测试、清理等操作。\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Go toolchain\n- Python 3.11+\n- Docker (for container builds)\n\n## Related Changes\n\nNone\n\n## Implementation Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n## Deferred Items\n\n[To be filled during implementation]"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/scripts/release.sh":[]},"diff":"Index: /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md\n===================================================================\n--- /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md\n+++ /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-033/CHANGE.md\n@@ -5,27 +5,180 @@\n - **Title**: Makefile 构建目标体系\n - **Module**: root\n - **Language**: Makefile\n - **Size**: M\n-- **Status**: Not Started\n+- **Status**: Completed\n \n ## Description\n \n Makefile 构建目标体系，用于统一管理项目的构建、测试、清理等操作。\n \n ## Dependencies\n \n-- Go toolchain\n-- Python 3.11+\n-- Docker (for container builds)\n+- Go toolchain 1.25+\n+- Python 3.10+\n+- Docker 20.10+ (for container builds)\n+- GNU Make 4.0+\n \n ## Related Changes\n \n None\n \n ## Implementation Notes\n \n-[To be filled during implementation]\n+### Files Created\n \n+#### Core Files\n+- **Makefile** - Root Makefile with all main targets and variables\n+- **VERSION** - Version file for trac